In this question distance of centre of mass of new disc is $\alpha R$ not $\frac{\alpha}{R}$.
$\begin{aligned}
& -\frac{3 \mathrm{M}}{4} \alpha \mathrm{R}+\frac{\mathrm{M}}{4} \mathrm{R}=0 \\
